6. Issues with this Infrastructure

SPOF (Single Point of Failure):

If the server fails, the website goes offline.

Downtime during Maintenance:

Updating code may require restarting the web or application server.

Scalability Limitations:

A single server cannot handle very high traffic; performance may drop.
